org.openpnp.spi

Interface LinearInputAxis

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Axis, Identifiable, Named, PropertySheetHolder, Solutions.Subject, WizardConfigurable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ControllerAxis
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractControllerAxis, AbstractSingleTransformedAxis, ReferenceCamClockwiseAxis, ReferenceCamCounterClockwiseAxis, ReferenceControllerAxis, ReferenceMappedAxis

    public interface LinearInputAxis
extends Axis
    A LinearInputAxis is either directly a controller axis or something transformed by one of the "mechanical" transformations. This Interface serves as the distinction, so only one level of linear transformation can be set up.
